Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:11.38,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是連前進軌道都無法改變的幾率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:15.88,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有百分之一就要奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟、被「命運」所束縛的人生、不 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:26.39,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要將它重寫、因為若能看見你和未來 不是最棒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:29.52,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧！我只想在戰鬥中成長 HEY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.36,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,擊穿陰天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:33.53,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我的烈焰仍舊熊熊燃燒 雷鳴撕裂天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:37.36,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想消除夢魘 看見未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:39.87,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,過去、未來、還有如今當下、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.83,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不畏懼過去 現在為了被托付的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.20,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吼出我的驕傲!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:50.88,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想看到眼淚、所以要不斷嘶吼！一直永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.84,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會墮落！因為揚起的風會讓我凌駕於命運之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:02:01.22,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為身後、有著想要守護的笑容！ 永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,為了彼此！我會揍飛你心中的痛苦！讓悲傷什麼的永遠安息！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:08.85,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,832)}無論多少次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:34.87,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,月光搖曳 我們未來的藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:42.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會實現 描繪明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.92,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠不會磨滅 銘記在心中的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:55.72,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,若是無盡的淚水能掩蓋傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:04.77,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,那就無需畏懼 再次去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:13.24,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向著無邊無際的天空 張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:19.08,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再哭泣 仰望天空中那輪皎月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:24.92,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,即使心存悲傷 也要懷著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.26,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算無法回頭 也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:35.89,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生輝的夢想 閃耀在探索的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:41.89,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最寶貴的那份思念 仍舊在延續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:47.73,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,無論哪裏 我們都一起走過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:55.53,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,825)}握住那唯一的心靈之匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7頭龍從日蝕的大門中走出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了守護未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7位滅龍魔法師與龍開始戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在拉開序幕的是 龍的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:41.47,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(524,0)\pos(646,520)}人對人、龍對龍、人對龍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大塊頭 別小看了雷神眾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也是生物 就一定會感受到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗文字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精機槍 妖精群舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重粒子陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 吃了這麼多招的感覺不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用 沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之獄炎會將魔法燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 真是笑不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓拉克薩斯對付它還真是不適合啊 火和雷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有水之滅龍魔法師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒聽說有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火的話這裏倒是有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了哦 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下去吧 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到你了 炎之龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 汝是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是夏 我現在要把你吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事誰都不會想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了要吃掉你就會吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是美味的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 你這傢伙打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…就…交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給你？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去城堡那邊 拉克薩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去幫助溫蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確 溫蒂雖然是滅龍魔法師 但還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有她一個人的話 會很吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克薩斯 我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之龍 就交給炎之滅龍魔法師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那傢伙交給你沒有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我要把這傢伙吃掉提升我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們去城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適可而止吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休要激怒吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說要吞掉吾之火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區人類大言不慚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此等感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是此等感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍王 伊古尼魯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟…和伊古尼魯是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊古尼魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道伊古尼魯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之友人 亦是火龍王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊古尼魯是我的老爹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 這究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是未來的我的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看別人的日記 還真是個好興趣啊 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 順便看一下我的調教日記怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是無視我嗎 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是龍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的破壞力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了這個力量 就一定能殺掉阿庫諾羅基亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後由我來支配這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎裂吧 大地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒吧 天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消逝吧 生命的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是龍之王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於龍王祭誕生的新生之王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影將在這裏成為光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為絕對之光 照亮世間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不需要這種骯髒不堪的光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的光存在於我們自己心中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑你那微弱的光 根本就什麼都找不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼夏會騎在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿特拉斯費雷姆 你背叛了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾只順從吾心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊古尼魯之子 便是我友人之子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿特拉斯費雷姆 你背叛了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾只順從吾心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊古尼魯之子 便是我友人之子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的操龍魔法居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什麼 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我的意識被魔法阻斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是成為了朋友而已 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然說…朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 從背後繞過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莎古雷亞 小心背後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆哮無法撼動吾之火焰之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰無法摧毀我的金鋼之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休要小覷吾之獄炎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地獄中噴涌而出的巨人之焰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 吃掉了巨人之焰的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之友人的龍之炎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…吃掉了阿特拉斯費雷姆的火焰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍和龍在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好厲害 但為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經美麗的花之都如今鮮血四濺 一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人與龍與魔的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人與人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍與龍戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人與龍戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這正是古代的災厄 龍王祭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您振作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無…無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都無法復原了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶造型 冰凍的黑雷之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雜亂的風牙之社
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙 沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種數量 這種威壓感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在於我的記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰雙劍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒了你的這個招數 還記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那我就不客氣地使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 特洛伊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使沒有蕾比 我們也是車道·引擎小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼天翔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物亂舞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能上啊 特洛伊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫色之焰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父子的火焰攻擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 我也不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的煙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上鉤了 怪物們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像中的還要不服老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷神的荷電粒子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這是第幾隻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巖鐵壁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳩拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巖山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為敵人是很棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作為同伴 沒有人比他更可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就封住你的行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西根本沒效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是認真攻擊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就行了吧 羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是贏不了龍的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們被命令只是不能殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是另一個可能性的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既是你的影子 也是你心中的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 閉嘴 閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實呆著就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個絕望的世界裏 只有你能倖存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 成為王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼 我不想成為王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是聽誰的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是你自己嗎 羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:18:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召喚了我們龍 想要成為世界之王的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是七年後的你的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受吧 你的心將會被黑暗侵染
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是今後必定會被侵染吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運只能接受 你不會死在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間回溯 一個小時前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西…呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自稱羅格…七年後的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是另一個未來人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把露西…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格看來成長為了厲害的魔法師了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 說是未來就有弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉這個時代的羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來羅格的存在也會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 根據時間悖論
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來羅格存在著 也即證明過去的羅格絕對不會被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有這種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是時間正常流轉的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在時間混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來露西以及知曉時間混亂的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都變成了打破正常的虛數
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉現在的羅格 未來的羅格會被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來羅格被消滅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裏的露西也許也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來羅格由我來打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一味憑意氣用事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來羅格是在哪裏走錯了路 他不是現在的羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的羅格沒有任何罪孽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要將他殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也要走錯路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會對現在的羅格出手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 已經束手無策了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格變成了這次事件的整體關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說 羅格沒有從未來過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門不會被打開 龍也不會來襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓世界復原 必須殺死羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 大叔的火真心好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 龍的火果然比一般貨要好吃麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你問的還真好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話題要說起來就長了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之炎的高品質簡直讓我神魂顛倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你所謂的說來話長麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長年釀成的醇香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像開啟了一個很奇怪的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 罪孽與犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 大叔火焰的風味就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 後續我下次再聽好了

